In entrepreneurship it is often said you will strike gold if you are driven by passion and do what you love doing as a business. Here at k24 business we have been at the forefront of highlighting Kenyans who have set the example by shaping their destinies, providing employment for many in the country and most importantly showing that no matter the unfortunate circumstances one grows up in they can make it in life. In line with the International Women’s Day to be marked on Thursday we have dedicated this week’s episode of Destiny Shapers to the amazing women that have put their fears aside and created empires for their brands.  